id: pmc-jk1a
title: Final release verification and npm publication audit
description: "Continue the pm-changelog production-readiness pass by rerunning release gates, temp-folder install verification, strict pm validation, GitHub release checks, changelog self-generation, git commit/push state, and npm publication/auth status."
