close_reason: Final verification is complete for all locally controllable release readiness work; npm publication remains blocked by missing registry authentication and is documented in pmc-ek6t.
body: "## Scope\\n\\nThis item records the final continuation pass requested for pm-changelog after the initial release-readiness work. It covers local release gates, independent install verification, pm governance validation, GitHub release/repository verification, and npm publication status.\\n\\n## Constraints\\n\\nThe package can be validated, committed, pushed, and released on GitHub from this machine. npm publication requires npm registry credentials authorized to create or publish the unscoped pm-changelog package name."
